commit message:
Merge pull request #473 from Imkal/patch-1

Update res/values-fr/strings.xml

Merge pull request #36 from eleybourn/master

Sync with master, including translations
Fix to FR strings (apostrophe without backslash)

Handle broken android versions that do not accept null number format for
progress dialogs
Ensure default bookshelf is really set.
Prevent editing series and formats in list if empty

Fix duplicate series problem

Series of the form 'SomeName(2)' and 'SomeName(2.0)' are different, but
becuase series_num in the database was an integer, the 2.0 was being
coerced into a '2', resulting in a duplicate index error.

The series_num column has been changed to 'text'. This should not affect
booklist sorting as the existing code casts it to a float for sorting
purposes.
